  "prompt": "Which cheat codes are available for Brave Frontier, and what do they do?",
  "response": "As of my knowledge cutoff in October 2023, **Brave Frontier** does not feature traditional cheat codes that players can enter to gain immediate in-game advantages. However, the game has offered various **promotional codes** and **event-related codes** that grant players special rewards. Below is an overview of the types of codes that have been available and how they function:\n\n### 1. **Promotional Codes**\n\nThese codes are typically released by the game's developers during special events, collaborations, or anniversaries. Redeeming these codes can provide players with a range of rewards, such as:\n\n- **Gems**: The in-game premium currency used for summoning units, improving equipment, and more.\n- **Exclusive Units**: Rare or powerful characters that can be added to your roster.\n- **Equipment and Items**: Gear that can strengthen your units or provide other in-game benefits.\n- **Boosters**: Temporary enhancements that can aid in battles or resource gathering.\n\n**How to Redeem Promotional Codes:**\n\n1. **Launch Brave Frontier** and navigate to the **Settings** menu.\n2. Look for an option labeled **\"Redeem Code\"**, **\"Promotions\"**, or something similar.\n3. **Enter the promotional code** exactly as provided, paying attention to capitalization and any special characters.\n4. **Confirm** to receive your rewards.\n\n### 2. **Event Codes**\n\nDuring specific in-game events or community activities, **event codes** may be distributed to participants. These codes often provide:\n\n- **Event-Specific Rewards**: Items or units tied to the theme of the event.\n- **Experience Boosts**: Temporary increases to experience points gained.\n- **Unique Skins or Customizations**: Cosmetic items to personalize your units or interface.\n\n**Redeeming Event Codes** generally follows the same process as promotional codes, accessed through the game's settings or a dedicated event section.\n\n### 3. **Social Media and Community Codes**\n\nDevelopers occasionally release codes through their **official social media channels** such as Twitter, Facebook, or Discord. These are often part of:\n\n- **Giveaways**: Contests or random draws where codes are awarded to participants.\n- **Announcements**: New updates or features accompanied by exclusive rewards.\n- **Community Milestones**: Celebrations when the game reaches certain player or achievement milestones.\n\n**To Access These Codes:**\n\n1. **Follow Brave Frontier's official social media accounts** to stay updated.\n2. **Participate in community events** or discussions where codes might be shared.\n3. **Check official announcements** for any new code releases.\n\n### 4. **Developer and Partner Codes**\n\nSometimes, codes are distributed through collaborations with other brands or platforms. These might offer:\n\n- **Cross-Promotional Items**: Rewards that tie into both Brave Frontier and the partner brand.\n- **Special Bundles**: Packages that include multiple types of rewards for a single code.\n\n**Usage is similar to promotional and event codes**, accessed through the game's code redemption interface.\n\n### **Caution and Best Practices**\n\n- **Avoid Unofficial Cheats and Hacks**: Third-party tools or websites claiming to provide cheat codes can jeopardize your account's security and violate Brave Frontier's terms of service, potentially leading to bans.\n  \n- **Verify Sources**: Always obtain codes from **official channels** to ensure their legitimacy and safety.\n  \n- **Stay Updated**: Developers may discontinue certain codes or make time-limited releases, so regularly check official communications to not miss out on new opportunities.\n\n### **Where to Find Current Codes**\n\n- **Official Website**: [Brave Frontier Official Site](https://www.bravefrontier.com) (check the news or promotions section)\n  \n- **Social Media**:\n  - [Brave Frontier Twitter](https://twitter.com/BraveFrontier)\n  - [Brave Frontier Facebook](https://www.facebook.com/BraveFrontier)\n\n- **Community Forums**: Engage with other players on forums or Discord servers where members might share newly discovered or officially released codes.\n\n### **Final Thoughts**\n\nWhile Brave Frontier may not support traditional cheat codes, the availability of promotional and event-related codes provides ample opportunities to enhance your gameplay legally and safely. Always prioritize obtaining codes through trustworthy sources to maintain the integrity and security of your gaming experience.",
